<headline>Special Weather Statement issued January 09 at 2:49PM MST  by NWS GreatFalls</headline>
<description>...Heavy snow bands will impact interstate 15 from Dell to Monida
Pass through 345 PM MST...
At 246 PM MST, Doppler radar was tracking heavy snow bands along a
line extending from 25 miles northeast of Monida to 9 miles west of
Lima.
HAZARD...Heavy snow and wind gusts up to 30 mph
SOURCE...Radar indicated.
IMPACT...Reduced visibility down to a half mile or less and slippery
roads.
Locations impacted include...
Lima, Monida, Dell, Snowline, and Monida Pass.
MAX HAIL SIZE...0.00 IN
MAX WIND GUST...&lt;30 MPH</description>
<instruction>Slow Down and be prepared for reduced visibility and slippery roads.</instruction>
